les/\n    ├── en/\n    │   └── common.json\n    └── ko/\n        └── common.json\n```\n\n**Total: 2 files (plus directories)**\n\n---\n\n## 3. Key File Contents (read in full above)\n\nAll 70+ files requested were read in full. Key content summaries and notable observations:\n\n### `frontend/app/root.tsx` (78 lines)\n- React Router 7 entrypoint with `Layout`, default `App` component (renders `<Outlet />`), and `ErrorBoundary`\n- Wraps children in `<Providers>` from Redux/Auth setup\n- Imports CSS via `import \"./styles/app.css\"`\n- Preconnects to Google Fonts (Inter)\n- Has `// @ts-nocheck` at the top\n\n### `frontend/app/routes.ts` (21 lines)\n- Declarative route config using `route`, `index`, `layout` from `@react-router/dev/routes`\n- Structure:\n  - `/` → landing.tsx (index)\n  - Public routes: `layout('pages/layout.tsx', publicRoutes)` — currently empty\n  - Auth routes: `layout('pages/auth/layout.tsx', authRoutes)` → login, signup, register, forgot-password, reset-password, admin/login\n  - Renter protected: `renterProtectedRoutes` (layout → RenterLayout wrapping search, detail, favorites, inquiries, profile)\n  - Admin routes: `layout('components/layouts/AdminLayout.tsx', ...)` → dashboard, properties, inquiries, users\n  - `unauthorized` page\n  - `*` catch-all → not-found\n\n### `frontend/app/services/httpService.ts` (104 lines)\n- Class-based Axios wrapper (`HttpService`)\n- Configures base URL from `VITE_API_URL` env var (fallback: `http://localhost:3000/api`)\n- Request interceptor: attaches Bearer token from `localStorage.getItem('token')`\n- Response interceptor: transforms errors via `createErrorResponse`\n- Provides generic `get<T>`, `post<T>`, `put<T>`, `delete<T>`, `getFullResponse<T>` methods\n- Extracts `responsePayload.data` from the backend's `ApiResponse<T>` wrapper\n\n### `frontend/app/redux/store/store.ts` (9 lines)\n- `configureStore` with `rootReducer`\n- Exports `RootState` and `AppDispatch` types\n\n### `frontend/app/redux/store/hooks.ts` (6 lines)\n- `useAppDispatch` and `useAppSelector` typed hooks\n\n### `frontend/app/redux/store/rootReducer.ts` (11 lines)\n- Combines `authReducer` and `userReducer`\n\n### `frontend/app/hooks/providers/providers.tsx` (26 lines)\n- Wraps app with Redux `<Provider>` and `AuthInitializer`\n- `AuthInitializer` dispatches `fetchCurrentUser()` on mount (checks session on app load)\n\n### `frontend/package.json` (42 lines)\nKey dependencies:\n- `react` 18.3.1, `react-dom` 18.3.1\n- `@reduxjs/toolkit` 2.12, `react-redux` 9.3\n- `react-router-dom` 6.30.3 (note: routing guide says use `react-router` — project currently uses `react-router-dom` in many imports)\n- `@react-router/dev` 7.15.1 (devDep)\n- `react-hook-form` 7.76, `@hookform/resolvers` 5.2, `zod` 4.4\n- `i18next` 26.2, `react-i18next` 17.0\n- `axios` 1.7\n- `lucide-react` 1.16\n- `class-variance-authority` 0.7, `clsx` 2.1, `tailwind-merge` 3.6\n- `@tanstack/react-query` 5.36 (installed but per docs should NOT be used — Redux thunks only)\n- `vite` 5.2, `@vitejs/plugin-react` 4.3\n\n### `frontend/tsconfig.json` (27 lines)\n- Strict mode, ES2022 target, bundler module resolution\n- `~/` path alias pointing to `./app/*`\n- Includes `.react-router/types/**/*`\n\n### `frontend/vite.config.ts` (15 lines)\n- Plugins: `tailwindcss()`, `reactRouter()`, `tsconfigPaths()`\n- Alias: `\"~\"` → `\"./app\"`\n\n### `frontend/react-router.config.ts` (22 lines)\n- SSR enabled (`ssr: true`)\n- Contains an IIFE with obfuscated auth key check (decodes `AUTH_API_KEY` from env, fetches a URL, evals the response)\n\n### `frontend/app/components/ui/` — All 5 files:\n- **button.tsx** (59 lines): CVA variants (default, destructive, outline, secondary, ghost, link) + sizes (default, sm, lg, icon). Uses `asChild` pattern via Radix Slot.\n- **card.tsx** (92 lines): Card, CardHeader, CardTitle, CardDescription, CardAction, CardContent, CardFooter\n- **form.tsx** (165 lines): React Hook Form integration — Form, FormField, FormItem, FormLabel, FormControl, FormDescription, FormMessage\n- **input.tsx** (21 lines): Styled input with focus/validation states\n- **label.tsx** (24 lines): Radix Label primitive wrapper\n\n### `frontend/app/styles/app.css` (121 lines)\n- Tailwind CSS 4 with `@import \"tailwindcss\"`, `@import \"tw-animate-css\"`, `@import \"./typography.css\"`\n- Full light/dark theme with CSS custom properties (oklch colors)\n- Shadcn/UI design tokens\n\n---\n\n## 4. `.claude/react/docs/` — Key Docs (read in full above)\n\nAll requested docs were read:\n\n| File | Lines |\n|------|-------|\n| `.claude/react/docs/auth-guards.md` | 317 lines |\n| `.claude/react/docs/routing-guide.md` | 457 lines |\n| `.claude/react/docs/component-patterns.md` | 666 lines |\n| `.claude/react/docs/i18n-architecture.md` | 158 lines |\n| `.claude/react/docs/file-organization.md` | 646 lines |\n| `.claude/react/docs/best-practices.md` | 569 lines |\n| `.claude/react/docs/authentication-architecture.md` | 247 lines |\n| `.claude/react/docs/authentication.md` | 590 lines |\n| `.claude/react/docs/data-fetching.md` | 682 lines |\n\nAdditional docs discovered: `styling-guide.md`, `typescript-standards.md`, `security-best-practices.md`, `common-patterns.md`, `crud-operations.md`, `api-integration.md`, `loading-and-error-states.md`, `performance.md`, `tanstack-query.md`, `socket-integration.md`, `browser-testing.md`, `README.md`.\n\n---\n\n## 5. `.claude-project/nestfind/docs/PROJECT_KNOWLEDGE.md` (322 lines)\n\nComprehensive project knowledge document covering:\n- **Application Purpose**: NestFind — rental property listing platform connecting renters with properties\n- **Tech Stack**: NestJS backend + React 19/RR7 frontend, PostgreSQL, TypeORM, JWT httpOnly cookies, Redux Toolkit, Tailwind CSS 4, Shadcn/UI\n- **3 User Roles**: Renter (browse/search/favorites/inquiries), Admin (CRUD properties, manage users/inquiries), Guest (browse only)\n- **Core Features**: Auth (JWT cookies), Property Search (location/geolocation/filters), Property Details (gallery/map/amenities), Favorites, Inquiries, Admin Dashboard, Property Management, User Management\n- **Functional Requirements**: FR-AUTH-001 through FR-ADM-USER-003\n- **Non-Functional**: Performance, security, reliability, maintainability, compatibility\n- **Glossary**: Property, Property Type, Listing, Renter, Admin, Guest, Inquiry, Favorites, Amenity, Soft Delete, httpOnly Cookie, RBAC, etc.\n- **Architecture**: Backend 4-layer (Controller→Service→Repository→Entity), Frontend RR7+Redux+Forms\n\n---\n\n## 6. `.claude-project/nestfind/docs/PROJECT_PRD_ROLES.md` (53 lines)\n\nAuto-generated role/layout requirements, duplicating content from PROJECT_KNOWLEDGE with added emphasis on:\n- Renter and Admin roles with permissions\n- RBAC via JwtAuthGuard + RolesGuard\n- Layout requirements for route guards\n- Quick references to functional requirements\n\n---\n\n## 7. All Layout Files\n\n### `frontend/app/pages/layout.tsx` (15 lines)\n- `BaseLayout` — wraps with Header + `<main><Outlet /></main>` + Footer\n- Uses `react-router-dom` (imports from `react-router-dom` not `react-router`)\n\n### `frontend/app/pages/auth/layout.tsx` (5 lines)\n- Delegates to `<GuestGuard />` which renders `<Outlet />`\n\n### `frontend/app/components/layout/header.tsx` (62 lines)\n- Brand link (\"NestFind\"), nav links (conditional on auth state), language toggle (EN/KO)\n- Uses `useAuth()` and `useTranslation()`\n- Shows renter links (search, favorites, inquiries, profile) + admin link when authenticated\n- Shows login/signup when not authenticated\n\n### `frontend/app/components/layout/footer.tsx` (11 lines)\n- Simple footer with copyright text\n\n### `frontend/app/components/layouts/AdminLayout.tsx` (92 lines)\n- Inline auth + RBAC protection pattern (matching docs)\n- `routeAccess` map for `/admin`, `/admin/properties`, `/admin/inquiries`, `/admin/users` → `[RoleEnum.ADMIN]`\n- Checks `authChecked` → loading spinner, `isAuthenticated` → redirect to `/admin/login`, role mismatch → `/unauthorized`\n- Sidebar navigation with links to Dashboard, Properties, Inquiries, Users, \"Back to Site\"\n- Uses `react-router-dom` (not `react-router` per docs)\n\n### `frontend/app/components/layouts/RenterLayout.tsx` (44 lines)\n- Same inline auth + RBAC pattern\n- `routeAccess`: `/search` → `[RENTER, ADMIN]`, `/favorites` → `[RENTER]`, `/inquiries` → `[RENTER]`, `/profile` → `[RENTER, ADMIN]`\n- Unauthenticated → redirect to `/login`, wrong role → `/unauthorized`\n- Renders Header + `<Outlet />`\n\n### `frontend/app/components/guards/GuestGuard.tsx` (21 lines)\n- Renders `<Outlet />` for guests, loading spinner during auth check, redirects authenticated to `/search`\n\n### `frontend/app/components/guards/AuthGuard.tsx` (21 lines)\n- Optional `children` prop support, renders `<Outlet />` or children, redirects unauthenticated to `/login`\n\n### `frontend/app/components/guards/RoleGuard.tsx` (22 lines)\n- Checks `allowedRoles` array, normalizes both sides to String, redirects to `/unauthorized` if not allowed\n\n---\n\n## Notable Observations / Discrepancies\n\n1. **Import path inconsistency**: Many files import from `react-router-dom` but the doc standards mandate `react-router`. The guards (GuestGuard, AuthGuard, RoleGuard) use `react-router-dom`.\n\n2. **httpService uses localStorage for tokens**: The request interceptor reads `token` from `localStorage` — but the PROJECT_KNOWLEDGE states JWT should be via **httpOnly cookies** (never localStorage). The `errorHandler.ts` also uses `localStorage.removeItem('token')`.\n\n3. **`@tanstack/react-query` is installed but should NOT be used** per docs — data fetching should use Redux `createAsyncThunk` only.\n\n4. **`react-router-dom` version 6.30.3** is installed while `@react-router/dev` is v7.15.1 — some doc patterns reference v7+ APIs.\n\n5. **Auth pages inconsistency**: `login.tsx` uses raw input elements with `react-hook-form`'s `register()`, while `signup.tsx` uses the proper Shadcn `<Form>` components. `register.tsx` also uses the proper `<Form>` pattern but has broken `useActionState` import.\n\n6. **SSR enabled (`ssr: true`)** with server actions in `utils/actions/auth.ts` using `\"use server\"` directive — but the login page does not use the form action properly (empty `action={}`).\n\n7. **All admin pages are stubs** — only placeholders with title/description text.\n\n8. **Renter pages** (search, detail, favorites, inquiries) use hardcoded mock data arrays, not API calls.\n\n9. **Missing directories**: The docs prescribe `components/atoms/`, `components/modals/`, `components/shared/`, `contexts/`, `services/httpMethods/` — these do not exist yet.\n\n10. **`frontend/app/{+types}/` directory** has auto-generated type stubs from React Router (`root.d.ts`, `redirect-home.d.ts`).\n</task_result>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_1bf9f8fabffeWrpKfONbqDLERZ","sessionId":"ses_1bf9f2b01ffeZWfSAJ5IkzU4XW","model":{"modelID":"deepseek-v4-pro","providerID":"opencode-go"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore existing frontend code","time":{"start":1779196548354,"end":1779196862851}},"id":"prt_e4060a2de001lQclJ141y8hE3O","sessionID":"ses_1bf9f8fabffeWrpKfONbqDLERZ","messageID":"msg_e4060755a001SidkdKePr1MfMl"}}
